Directed by Omkar.

Written by Omkar. Karthik Rajan. Abburi Ravi. Ranjith Sankar.

Cast Samantha Ruth Prabhu(Amrutha (as Samantha Akkineni)). Nagarjuna Akkineni(Rudra). Vennela Kishore(Kishore). Abhinaya(Kiran). Rao Ramesh(Amrutha’s Father). Shatru(Goon). Vidyullekha Raman(Chef). V.K. Naresh(Church Pastor (as Naresh)). Tejaswi Madivada(Ashwin’s Girlfriend). Seerat Kapoor(Suhanisa).Avinash. Ravi Varma(Sathi). Annapoorna(Landowner (as Annapoorna Amma)). Ashwin Babu(Ashwin). Satya Krishnan(College Lecturer). Mukhtar Khan(Police Inspector).Jayavani. Shakalaka Shankar(Yesu). Devan(College Principal).Rocket Raghava. Praveen(Ravi). Nandu Vijay Krishna(Nandu (as Anand)).Jagan Mohan Vancha.Shashidhar.Swapnika.Jabardasth Durgarao.Suresh Varma.Geetha Singh.Mukesh Makhija.Chintu.Mahesh.Bhavana.Sandeep.Bhupal Raj.Gayathri. Nandu(Anand).Nani.Meghana.Aditya.Lakshmipani Kanth.Master Rohan.Ramu.Saketh.Baby Lasya.Krishnateja.Shravan.Koteshwara Rao.Apparao.Naveen Chamki.Shruthi.Phani Basant

Language Telugu.

Producers Kavin Anne. Naren. Param V. Potluri. Pearl V. Potluri. Prasad V. Potluri.

Production Matinee Entertainments. Oak Entertainments. PVP Cinema.
